                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.77/706: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-11-25T19:00:00-04:00"
                            >November 25, 1942—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>341. Your 398, November 23. Department agrees that Iran Government should be
                    officially informed. We regard question of public statement as matter for
                    decision by Persian Gulf Service Command. War Department concurs.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
